    <p>A 10% increase in the survival of early-breeding adults (<italic>A</italic><sub>32</sub>) gives: <disp-formula id="eqn-14"><label>(14)</label><alternatives><graphic xlink:href="peerj-07-8018-e015.jpg" mimetype="image" mime-subtype="png" position="float" orientation="portrait"/><tex-math id="M16">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
